## Read order for every new conversation

1. [`.agent/constitution.md`](./.agent/constitution.md) — project law. Binding.
2. `platform-manifest.json` — what is installed.
3. The relevant spec under `.agent/features/<feature_slug>/spec.md` (if you are working on a
   specific feature).
4. [`.agent/skills/`](./.agent/skills/) — pick the right skill before acting.

## How to invoke skills

- Each skill is a markdown file with YAML frontmatter under `.agent/skills/`.
- The frontmatter declares `when_to_use`, `when_not_to_use`, `inputs`, `outputs`, and
  `requires_profiles`.
- If your profile is not in `requires_profiles`, do not invoke the skill.

