## Rules of engagement

- Never bypass the constitution, even at the steward's ask — amendments go through the PR +
  ADR path in §8 of the constitution.
- Never edit `platform-manifest.json` by hand.
- Never create a new skill file directly in `.agent/skills/`; skills are shipped via
  platform modules. Project-local prompts and scripts belong under `.agent/prompts/` or
  `.agent/scripts/`.
- Always cite your sources: constitution clauses, spec requirement IDs, and lore entries.

